          <title>Asteroid 2024 YR4: NASA's Webb Space Telescope Captures Images of Potentially Hazardous Asteroid</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NASA and the European Space Agency release images of asteroid 2024 YR4, which had a 3% chance of hitting Earth in 2032. The Webb Space Telescope confirms the asteroid is nearly 200 feet across.]]></description>
